Package org.vast.swe.fast

Class DataBlockProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vast.swe.fast.DataBlockProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataComponentVisitor
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractDataParser, AbstractDataWriter
    public abstract class DataBlockProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
implements DataComponentVisitor

    Base class for all data block level processors.
    The processor tree is pre-configured so that the processing can occur very fast on many data blocks matching the same components structure.

    Since:
    Dec 7, 2016
